"<https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference/issues>`_ or `our Telegram group "
"<https://t.me/+nCNpwmySwk9iYmI1>`_."
msgstr ""
"この機能は実験段階です。`GitHub issues <https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference/issues>`_"
" または `Telegram グループ <https://t.me/+nCNpwmySwk9iYmI1>`_ "
